## Unit 3: Lesson 24 - Chained Conditionals

# Background
To make chatbots respond to user input, you must evaluate both the user input and keywords within the input. More complex conditionals - chained if-statements - will enable your chatbot program to generate unique responses based a specific set of keywords. Chained conditionals are used to create multiple alternative conditions.  

# Lesson

* Examine the impact of order in chained if-statements.
* Create an interactive chatbot with if-else-if statements. 
  

